Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Filling in the distance between hate and love...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deductions and suspense of two people!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today, we're on the set of a drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The members of the cast are human too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Detective Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's stage, far away from human habitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this western-style house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mystery in which love and hatred entwine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The point of the case is color.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unconsciously chosen every time a person shops...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their own favorite color.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, even at the scene of a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, let us meet again at the end of the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has been Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, it was perfectly OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, you were so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though that last wink might have been a little much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:49.50,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,THE UNSEEN SUSPECT\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really saved us on this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The big-name actor who always does the opening prologue for this program...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He caught a cold, so we got thrown for a loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, please call me in to pinch-hit anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, I'm also willing to appear in this mystery drama as a special guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible, Detective{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, in the story this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's the widow that serves as the head of the household, her bitchy daughter, the decrepit butler...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:31.71,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kazami Yoshiki (28)\NRole of the Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:33.54,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Then, aside from the daughter's murdered husband and my role as a detective, no one beyond those five appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this about "bitchy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She isn't bitchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:41.05,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Namihara Kasumi (26)\NRole of the Daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:41.05,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,She's just established as a character who likes to be flashy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's bitchy because you're playing the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, Kazami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:52.10,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Akira (60)\NRole of the Butler
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.64,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Regarding the "decrepit" part, could you stop that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:53.27,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I only just turned 60, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not the age.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's your acting that I consider decrepit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:03:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although I hear you may have been a famous actor ages ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:11.41,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Nobuharu (31)\NRole of the Daughter's Husband
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:11.41,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Let's not quarrel before filming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:12.04,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Nobuharu (31)\NRole of the Daughter's Husband
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:12.96,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Kazami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you keep your cool too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, Ujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s late, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, by Ujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The former number one refreshing actress, Ujou Ruri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're gonna meet Ujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the one who nominated you as our stand-in on the prologue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know about being the former number one refreshing whatever, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not by that old spinster lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I would refuse it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a washed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:59.21,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ujou Ruri (37)\NRole of the Female Head of Household
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:57.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Urine-smelling little boy like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's really her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's even prettier in person than on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Mouri Kogorou, it's nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it seems it was you who requested me for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not the first time, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have we met somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even after seeing this beauty spot under my lips, you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beauty spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doigaki Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Ruri-ppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been such a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since middle school, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way... They're acquaintances...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no idea it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not with this new surname!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:06:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, back then, you wore those coke-bottle glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I become a fine woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You certainly did!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how come Ruri-ppe isn't married?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A beauty like you could have anyone you wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because I've always been head-over-heels for you, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, please stop joking—he'll take you seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that child is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, just some kid from the neighborhood, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm his daughter, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you're Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s-?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we were together from kindergarten all the way to middle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's still a mystery, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why the school's most talented girl, Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the school's naughtiest boy, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, were so much in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That they even got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were in love for that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, who was always cool toward others...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would get really upset when the opponent was Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} and rush at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why everyone around would make fun of them and say, "The lovers' quarrel has started again!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're still going at it even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's surprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the vulgar Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} is now a renowned detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we go! Scene 134, camera rehearsal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body in front of the fireplace is covered by a gray tablecloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hanging on the chair from this table...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the victim's black coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, found next to the body after rolling there, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon that was used to bludgeon the victim to death:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A golf club with a white cover attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I've already solved the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of airs are you putting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell us already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just who is the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we were really doing it, I'd reveal the trick at this point, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, those lines aren't in the script...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight, Detective Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Might I have you solve it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, why did the culprit cover the body with a tablecloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the culprit loved the victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they thought that just leaving the body like that would be hard to endure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's a coat hung on the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did they go to the trouble of using the tablecloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, the reason for that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the gray tablecloth seemed warmer than the black coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:58.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, you're not saying that's your answer, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just say the hint in the prologue?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, why would gray seem warmer than black?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even your friends didn't amount to much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, do it seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, spit out the truth, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible, impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For this degree of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was so simple a deduction that, against my better judgment, I acted as if it were difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The point is, it wasn't that the culprit wanted to cover the body with the tablecloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But rather that the culprit didn't want to cover the body with the black coat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since black is their favorite color.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit subconsciously believed that utilizing items of their favorite color...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would unintentionally draw suspicion towards them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, take a close look at the golf bag propped against the fireplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only the head of the club with the black cover has been caught and is sticking out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is evidence that the culprit was going to use the club with the black cover as the weapon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the middle of pulling it out, stopped and switched to white.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, if you recognize the fact that this room's furniture and curtains are uniformly black...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With this being due to the tastes of the head of the household...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is the one that's even wearing a black dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe, the female head of the household that you're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of Sleeping Kogorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You decisively hit the mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as the rumors say, right, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:10:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, it would've been better if you'd just taken it seriously from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected, the real thing is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A corpse doesn't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Nobuharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kasumi, did you switch to this guy as the next one after that scriptwriter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad—I guess that's still off the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't shape up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old man, is it really smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To say something like that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know all about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your secret meetings every night with your young lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who that woman is or where she's from I don't know for certain yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already got a pretty good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pretty damn good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with those faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's how it is, I don't care if this program fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be sleeping in the back room until the heat dies down, so just film scenes I don't appear in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the son of the main sponsor for-this program, a newspaper company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why he knows all kinds of secret information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Between the bad terms of the contract and that delinquent character becoming popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're taking in quite a sum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I didn't want to appear in a program with that guy as the star either, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An order came down from the agency telling me to appear due to the high ratings, so I reluctantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was able to see Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} for the first time in a while, so I guess it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's take a break for 30 minutes and start again after we're all relaxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They had a big quarrel over Worcestershire sauce versus soy sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad and Mom did?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back in elementary school, during the training for Home Economics...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They had a big battle over which to put on top of sunny-side-up fried eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} said that, because sunny-side-up fried eggs were western food, it should be Worcestershire sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} declared that, for the Japanese people, it should be soy sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It gets less and less understandable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why they got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then, when it came time to eat the food that was made...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They ate in exactly the same order, and the whole class had a big laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, they both said, "Stop copying me," and began to quarrel over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, I can't say whether they were right for each other or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough stories from long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, please keep telling more, more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it's snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, the weather report did say there was a chance of snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we all go outside and see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's only five minutes of the break left...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right, even if it's only five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the first snow of the season!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected, it's great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snow, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see Ruri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Ruri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought we came out here together, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:21.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no good—his pupils are dilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's already dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! Contact the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who did this horrible thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the type to make enemies, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, in this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be the case that the first one to discover the body would be the first to be suspected?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it—it wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I came in here, he was already covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Believe me, Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be fooled by her tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An actress' tears are one of the tools of her trade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Kasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if it keeps going like this, we'll end up being the ones suspected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:27.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is Kazami Yoshiki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 28 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death is exsanguination as a result of damage to his left carotid artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was probably attacked while sleeping on this sofa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When his neck was sliced with a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The approximate time of death was between 7:50 PM, when the victim came to this room to take a nap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To when his body was discovered at 8:20 PM—an interval of 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we came into this room while touring the house, he was snoring, sound asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just around 8:00, wasn't it, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Dad looked at his watch and remarked that he had fallen sound asleep within ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ohhh, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you had to look after my little brother the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kind of case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, is he an acquaintance of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How very nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Yokomizo from the Shizuoka Prefectural Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's great to finally be able to meet you, Mrs. Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:18:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you can say it's wrong, or you can also say it's not so wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's totally wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a just a joke, a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, by some chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the actress, Ujou Ruri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now that I think about it, you're also...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the heck's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That so many actors and actresses are gathered...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as if this is the filming of a drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because... That's exactly what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it was like this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this western-style house in the recesses of Mount Fuji, you were filming a mystery drama when...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A real murder case occurred, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like the story where the mummy hunter himself became the mummy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? In the 20 minutes after 8:00 PM, the time that the murder was thought to have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:19:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had taken a break from filming and all the staff had been in groups of two or more, and thus have alibis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those without an alibi are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who discovered the body, Ujou Ruri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those who claimed they were alone in their rooms checking lines in the script...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Namihara Kasumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Akira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Nagumo Nobuharu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could only have been one of you four, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Ujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In detail, tell us the state of the room when you discovered the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the break, along with Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}—no, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and his group, we were taking a look around the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, because snow started falling, we invited the staff to go outside to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the snow was so pretty, I wanted to show it to Kazami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, and came to this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} had become angry and sullen over some things that happened during filming...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:58.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when I opened the door, he was bloody and collapsed on the floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a joke, so I shook his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there was no response.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I finally realized he was dead, I screamed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing that scream, you three rushed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, for the time being, can we have you four undergo body searches in separate rooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite looking everywhere in this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't found the approximately 10-centimeter long blade used to slit Kazami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that, none of the four had anything like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just in case, we also searched the staff's belongings and thoroughly searched the other rooms, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only items in the kitchen that could have been the weapon were carving knives, a fruit knife, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A box-cutter from inside the staff toolbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no luminol reaction from any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the victim had on him was a pack of cigarettes, a lighter, and his wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're still searching the drainage outlets and the area around this house with a metal detector, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's been no report that they've found anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though we found what we think is the golf glove and the coat that the culprit used during the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why can't we find the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, since the glove and the coat were both props that were used for the drama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one was in the room where they had been left because of the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that anyone could have taken them easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, where are the four suspects now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're in the room with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, awaiting further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:22:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the criminal is one of these people...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Transporting the weapon somewhere far away is impossible in the short time frame of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though that's the ease, why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why can't the weapon be found?
